# Unreal Engine Specific
Binaries/
DerivedDataCache/
Intermediate/
Saved/
Build/

# Ignore Visual Studio / IDE files
*.sln
*.suo
*.opensdf
*.sdf
*.VC.db
*.VC.opendb
.vs/
.idea/

# Visual Studio component prefs (regenerated by UE when C++/plugin source is present)
.vsconfig

# Third-party Unreal plugins distributed as pre-built SDKs (not source-controlled;
# each dev/CI must drop them into VR_Project/Plugins/ from the upstream release).
# See README.md "Setup -> step 2" and the Devlog 2026-05-28 "Phase 2: Plugin
# install discipline" entry for the canonical install instructions.
VR_Project/Plugins/AgoraPlugin/

# Per-developer Unreal Insights profiling artifacts (e.g. UECommandLine.tracing.txt
# hardcodes the dev's LAN trace-host IP). Generated locally during perf passes.
VR_Project/Profiling/

# Web Dashboard — Node deps + local secrets.
Web_Dashboard/node_modules/
Web_Dashboard/.env

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db